Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:45.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}虽然想去好好梳理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:53.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}但唯独真正想传达的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:59.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}纠葛不清说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:05.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}轻轻地深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:14.00,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}愿这温柔的希望能持续到永久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:17.50,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}能否看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:20.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:26.73,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}指尖描绘出的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.81,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}能否传递到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:33.71,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}我愿今天也能继续欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:38.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}你明天也能充满笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:47.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}一定 一定
